{"tid":208053,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"小六女童長得可愛　色阿伯竟伸魔爪","createTime":"2017-04-19T09:35:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-19T09:59:25.000Z","uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5e0e920f8ba13542a9ab9f97fe6cecf99d21ca7e","tid":208053,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T09:35:56.000Z","msg":"基隆一名61歲曾姓男子，前年10月2日到桃園一處社區訪友時，見當時只有11歲、準備上學的小六女學生長得很可愛，竟從後方環抱，無視對方激烈反抗，強行撫摸其胸部，案經警方調閱監視器查獲曾男；桃園地檢署今依強制猥褻罪嫌將他起訴。（突發中心張沛森／桃園報導）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://giant.gfycat.com/UnluckyEnchantedAfricanparadiseflycatcher.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgiant.gfycat.com%2FUnluckyEnchantedAfricanparadiseflycatcher.gif&h=21778eef&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d30d2613e6a42adb623983bb2823109284fc898d","tid":208053,"uid":3747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T09:41:37.000Z","msg":"牠首?"},{"pid":"05102c130fc20633b258386d2a878d76825a8457","tid":208053,"uid":60535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T09:42:42.000Z","msg":"台灣最美的風景是人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7f85cfe7fe579e96f97afa9039fafb1e453b93d","tid":208053,"uid":56467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T09:59:25.000Z","msg":"咁今次係基隆全取三分？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}